title: The Brilliant 85 South Show feat. Andrew Schultz | Ep. 78

description:
Andrew was in Atlanta for a show at a diner, so we told him to stop through in his inbetween time. We talk about the white man, Serena Wililams and everything else going on in the world. Subscribe & share! Then go to the shop to get some merch! 85southshow.com/shop
